<div class="card">

<h2>About Us</h2>

<p>
Scaleculus is a Grade 11 STEM initiative focused on making calculus clear, interactive, and accessible.
</p>

<br>

<p>
Our website provides lessons, examples, and step-by-step guides to help students master limits, derivatives, integrals, and more.
</p>

<br>

<p>
Designed by students, for students, Scaleculus turns challenging calculus concepts into learning that’s both scalable and understandable.
</p>

